msgctxt "14517"
msgid "ワシが、覆面の男とちゃういうんか？"
msgstr "Am I supposed to be a masked man?"

msgctxt "14552"
msgid ""
"ああ。やつの剣が純粋な天念理心流だとすれば\n"
"アンタのはそこに我流の小太刀術を\n"
"取り入れたものだ。"
msgstr ""
"Oh. If his sword is pure Tennen Rishin-ryu, then you have adopted my own "
"style of swordsmanship."

msgctxt "14650"
msgid "そうじゃねえか？"
msgstr "Isn't it?"

msgctxt "14672"
msgid ""
"アンタの剣は覆面の男のものとは違った。\n"
"だが沖田……　なんで自分が覆面の男だなんて嘘を？"
msgstr ""
"Your sword was different from that of the masked man. But Okita ... Why do "
"you lie that you're a masked man?"

msgctxt "14761"
msgid ""
"……そらあ本物のお前と戦うためや。\n"
"どやった？　久しぶりに坂本龍馬として振った\n"
"剣の味は？"
msgstr ""
"...... Well, to fight the real you. How did you do it? What is the taste of "
"the sword you swung as Ryoma Sakamoto for the first time in a long time?"

msgctxt "14852"
msgid "……？"
msgstr "……？"

msgctxt "14859"
msgid ""
"ほんまの名前隠して生きるいうことは、\n"
"それまでの自分をなかったことにする、いうことや。"
msgstr ""
"To live by hiding your real name means to make yourself something you didn't"
" have before."

msgctxt "14946"
msgid ""
"坂本龍馬としての人生を自分から進んで\n"
"否定せなあかん。"
msgstr "Akan who is willing to deny his life as Ryoma Sakamoto."

msgctxt "15001"
msgid ""
"せやから一（はじめ）ちゃんは……\n"
"ワシと似た者同士なんや。"
msgstr "Sayakaraichi (Hajime) -chan is ... Someone who looks like an eagle."

msgctxt "15060"
msgid "似たもの同士……？"
msgstr "Similar things ...?"

msgctxt "15079"
msgid ""
"ヒヒ、なんでもあらへん。\n"
"せやけどええもんやったやろ？\n"
"坂本龍馬として戦うっちゅうのは。"
msgstr ""
"Baboon, no matter what. Yeah, did you do it? What is fighting as Ryoma "
"Sakamoto?"

msgctxt "15168"
msgid "ああ……　そうだったかもしれねえな。"
msgstr "Ah ... maybe that was the case."

msgctxt "15205"
msgid "フッ、感謝しいや。"
msgstr "Huh, thank you."

msgctxt "15224"
msgid ""
"だが……　アンタが覆面の男じゃねえなら、\n"
"なんで俺の正体を知っていたんだ？"
msgstr "But ... if you're not a masked man, why did you know me?"

msgctxt "15299"
msgid ""
"一（はじめ）ちゃんが近藤さんに会うた時、\n"
"ワシもあそこにおったんや。"
msgstr "When Ichi (Hajime) met Mr. Kondo, I was there too."

msgctxt "15368"
msgid "近藤さんに会お思うてな。"
msgstr "I hope to see Mr. Kondo."

msgctxt "15393"
msgid ""
"それで全部、盗み聞きしてたってわけか……\n"
"いい趣味だな。"
msgstr "That's why I was eavesdropping on everything ... It's a good hobby."

msgctxt "15450"
msgid ""
"心配せんでええ。\n"
"一（はじめ）ちゃんの正体は誰にも言わん。\n"
"近藤さんもその腹積もりや。"
msgstr ""
"Don't worry, yeah. I don't tell anyone what Ichi (Hajime) is. Mr. Kondo is "
"also hungry."

msgctxt "15546"
msgid "ん？　どないした？"
msgstr "Hmm? Did you go?"

msgctxt "15565"
msgid ""
"いや……　アンタも近藤も、\n"
"それに永倉も“覆面の男”じゃなかった。\n"
"なら、一体誰が……？"
msgstr ""
"No ... Neither you nor Kondo, nor Nagakura was a \"masked man\". Then who on"
" earth ...?"

msgctxt "15663"
msgid ""
"残るは土方、井上、藤堂……\n"
"そのうちの誰かってことか。"
msgstr "The rest are Hijikata, Inoue, Todo ... Who is that?"

msgctxt "15722"
msgid "お前が千石虎之丞だな……？"
msgstr "You're Toranosuke Sengoku ...?"

msgctxt "15749"
msgid "ま、待ってくれ！　斬らんでくれや！"
msgstr "Well, wait! Please cut it!"

msgctxt "15784"
msgid ""
"丸腰の相手を斬りはしねえ。\n"
"だが、屯所まで来てもらう。"
msgstr ""
"You can't slash your opponent with a round waist. However, I have him come "
"to the tunsho."

msgctxt "15839"
msgid "ひぃぃ！　堪忍してくれやぁ!!"
msgstr "Hi! Please be patient !!"

msgctxt "15868"
msgid ""
"いらん小芝居はもうええで。\n"
"千石はん。"
msgstr "Iran small play is Mouede. Sengoku Han."

msgctxt "15908"
msgid "……何や、遅いやないか沖田はん。"
msgstr "…… No, it ’s late, Han Okita."

msgctxt "15942"
msgid "……どういうことだ。"
msgstr "……What does it mean."

msgctxt "15963"
msgid ""
"さぁて、どういうことやと思う？\n"
"ヒヒ。"
msgstr "What do you think about it? Baboon."

msgctxt "16007"
msgid ""
"千石はんはなぁ、今回の作戦の協力者やった\n"
"っちゅうわけや。"
msgstr "Sengoku Hanha, I'm a collaborator of this operation."

msgctxt "16066"
msgid "なんだと？"
msgstr "what?"

msgctxt "16077"
msgid ""
"そういうこっちゃ。\n"
"ワシはあんたらが今晩乗り込んでくるっちゅう事を\n"
"知らされとったんや。"
msgstr "That kind of thing. I was informed that you were coming in tonight."

msgctxt "16166"
msgid ""
"せやから、勤王派の連中かき集めて、\n"
"さんざっぱら酒飲ませておいたんやでぇ。"
msgstr ""
"From Saya, I gathered up the Qin Wang sect and let them drink alcohol."

msgctxt "16241"
msgid ""
"おかげでだいぶ楽に斬れたやろ？\n"
"へへ、感謝しいや。"
msgstr ""
"Thanks to that, I was able to cut it quite easily? Thank you very much."

msgctxt "16294"
msgid ""
"ハナっからそういうからくりだったってわけか。\n"
"沖田、なぜ俺に黙ってた？"
msgstr ""
"I wonder if it was such a mechanism from Hana. Okita, why did you keep "
"silent to me?"

msgctxt "16365"
msgid "さあなあ。"
msgstr "Come on."

msgctxt "16377"
msgid ""
"新選組の皆さんはお仲間同士信用せんさかい……\n"
"ほれ、例の芹沢鴨もそうや。"
msgstr "The Shinsengumi members trust each other ... See, Serizawa Kamo, too."

msgctxt "16455"
msgid "身内に粛清されたんやったやろ？"
msgstr "Did you purge your relatives?"

msgctxt "16486"
msgid ""
"噂じゃ気に入らん店に火ぃつけるわ、\n"
"街中で大砲ぶっ放すわ……"
msgstr ""
"Rumor has it that I'll set fire to a store I don't like, I'll release a "
"cannon in the city ..."

msgctxt "16547"
msgid "えらい無茶する人やったらしいけどな。"
msgstr "I heard he did a great crazy person."

msgctxt "16584"
msgid "千石はん……　街の噂はアテんならんで？"
msgstr "Sengoku Han ... Isn't the rumor of the city awkward?"

msgctxt "16623"
msgid ""
"ハハッ！　それもそうや。\n"
"沖田はんが美少年やいうて騒いどったくらい\n"
"やからなあ！"
msgstr "Haha! That's right. Okita Han was so noisy as a young boy!"

msgctxt "16704"
msgid "あ？　そしたらワシが美少年ちゃういうんか……？"
msgstr "Ah? Then I'm a young boy ...?"

msgctxt "16751"
msgid ""
"な、なんや。冗談やって。\n"
"……それより沖田はん、約束の件、幕府への口利き、\n"
"忘れんと頼んまっせ。"
msgstr ""
"What? Just kidding. …… More than that, Han Okita, the promise, the talk to "
"the bakufu, and ask me to forget."

msgctxt "16848"
msgid ""
"てめえは……\n"
"そんなもんのために、勤王志士たちを\n"
"ハメたのか……？"
msgstr ""
"Temee ... Did you mess with the Qin Wang scholars for such a thing ...?"

msgctxt "16915"
msgid "ハハ！　ちょっとちゃうなあ。惜しいなあ。"
msgstr "Haha! I'm a little crazy. I'm sorry."

msgctxt "16956"
msgid ""
"……ワシがハメたんは志士たちだけとちゃうで？\n"
"あんたもや。……斎藤一はん。"
msgstr ""
"...... Isn't the eagle squirming only the scholars? You too. ...... Saito "
"Hajime."

msgctxt "17031"
msgid "なに……？"
msgstr "What……?"

msgctxt "17042"
msgid ""
"なあ沖田はん、そろそろワシにも\n"
"教えてくれてもええやろ？"
msgstr "Hey Okita, can you tell me about it?"

msgctxt "17099"
msgid ""
"何でワシぁ\n"
"こいつをここまで誘き出さなアカンかったんや。"
msgstr "Why didn't I invite this guy to this point?"

msgctxt "17157"
msgid "……べらべらようしゃべる奴やな、ほんま。"
msgstr "...... The guy who talks fluently, really."

msgctxt "17198"
msgid "お、沖田はん？"
msgstr "Oh, Okita Han?"

msgctxt "17214"
msgid "は……？"
msgstr "What ...?"

msgctxt "17223"
msgid "沖田！"
msgstr "Okita!"

msgctxt "17230"
msgid "ええ加減黙っとれや……！"
msgstr "Yeah, keep quiet ...!"

msgctxt "17255"
msgid "!!　な、な、何でや……"
msgstr "!! What, why ..."

msgctxt "17278"
msgid "沖田、お前……"
msgstr "Okita, you ..."

msgctxt "17293"
msgid "聞いたことないか？　……「鴨を語るべからず」。"
msgstr "Have you heard of it? ...... \"Don't talk about duck\"."

msgctxt "17340"
msgid "新選組の暗黙の掟や。せやからつい斬ってもうた。"
msgstr "The implicit rules of the Shinsengumi. I sang even if I slashed it."

msgctxt "17392"
msgid ""
"さぁて、千石はんの最後の質問……\n"
"その答え、一（はじめ）ちゃんには教えたろか。"
msgstr ""
"Well, the last question of Han Sengoku ... Did you tell Ichi (Hajime) -chan "
"the answer?"

msgctxt "17471"
msgid ""
"“何で千石はんは一（はじめ）ちゃんを\n"
"　ここまで誘き出さなアカンかったか”……"
msgstr "\"Why was Sengoku Hanhaichi (Hajime) -chan so uninvited?\" ..."

